title: William Dove
text: William Bathurst Dove (17 April 1872 – 14 August 1944) was an English <a href="golf">golf</a>er. He competed in the <a href="Golf%20at%20the%201900%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20individual">men's individual event</a> at the <a href="1900%20Summer%20Olympics">1900 Summer Olympics</a>.
